```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer / Agent
    participant Kernel as ArchenaKernel
    participant Pipeline as PipelineExecutor
    participant Skill as SkillRegistry
    participant Memory as MemoryManager
    participant LLM as LLMConnector

    Dev->>Kernel: Submit reasoning request ("Analyze context X")
    Kernel->>Pipeline: Build execution pipeline
    Pipeline->>Skill: Invoke ReasoningSkill
    Skill->>LLM: Call external model (OpenAI / Ollama)
    LLM-->>Skill: Return inference result
    Skill->>Memory: Store outcome (summary, embeddings)
    Memory-->>Kernel: Confirm persistence
    Kernel-->>Dev: Return processed response
```